						               													<description>Each of the participants of the game becomes one of the heroes of the Erenthi world, wandering around the vast lands on their own or with their allies in search of magical stones. The task of the player involves getting the treasure or thwart the other participants' plans. An important element of the game is defining an ally and an enemy, owing to how easier it is to win and eliminate the competition. Each round ends by dealing the award cards and establishing the wounds incurred during the round. The player who has gained the most stones wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the basic version of the game, in addition to good quality cards, you will find a magic code. On the publisher's website, you can activate it and receive a poster board and a map of the land delivered to your home. The board is not necessary for the game, but it is an accessory that helps to organize the place during the game. On the other hand, if you want to broaden your knowledge about the &amp;quot;flaming heart&amp;quot;, you can buy a collector's version of the game on the publisher's website.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
